      You can find the source code of this demo and instructions on how to run it yourself
      <a href="https://github.com/vaxine-io/examples/blob/main/basic_counter">on GitHub</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      But that's not all! To find out more about how geo-distribution affects latency for users, and how Vaxine can help with that
      — head over to our <a>advanced counter demo</a>
      . It will show you how the users around the world percieve the same application.
    </p>
  </div>
